record.text:
M’lady,

It has taken me some time to summon the courage to write you. Indeed I am of sovereign blood, but I am also just a man. Forgive my boldness, but there is an air of mystery about you that I very much wish to know.

Respectfully,
His Royal Highness Prince Farallel, Heir to the Praglish Throne
